original_title: Vickie Shaw: I'm Not Your Role Model
overview: A hysterical romp into the world of comedian Vicki Shaw, both on and off stage. Meet Vicki's partner Sgt. Patch, her kids and grand babies in their home in Houston. A rare and revealing look into Vicki's private life and what it takes to gear up for her sold-out show in Hollywood, California filmed to DVD
title: Vickie Shaw: I'm Not Your Role Model
